4 attempt to drive, run or attempt to run, molest or attempt to molest, flush or attempt to
5 flush, or harass or attempt to harass any such game with the use or aid of any
6 motor-driven vehicle. A person, other than the landowner, without the written
7 permission of the landowner or a lessee who actively farms or ranches that land, while
8 hunting big game or small game, other than waterfowl or cranes, statewide, may not
9 drive through any retired cropland, brush area, slough area, timber area, open prairie,
10 or unharvested or harvested cropland, except upon an established road or trail. The
11 provisions of this section relating to hunting big game or small game while using a
